'''普渡大学锅炉工队'''（Purdue Boilermaker）是美国[[普渡大学|普渡大学]]在[[NCAA|NCAA]]的代表队，下面有18支不同项目的分队，包括[[篮球|篮球]]、[[棒球|棒球]]、[[橄榄球|橄榄球]]、[[排球|排球]]、[[越野|越野]]和[[足球|足球]]等。它和同州的[[印第安纳大学|印第安纳大学]]的[[印第安纳大学山地人队|山地人队]]是全国闻名的德比宿敌<ref>{{cite news|last=Mathews|first=Jay|title=Top 12 Rivalries|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/2008/08/08/the-12-top-rivalries.html|accessdate=4 May 2012|newspaper=Newsweek|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501155327/http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/2008/08/08/the-12-top-rivalries.html|archive-date=2012-05-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Farestad-Rittel|first=Brandon|title=The 10 Best College Rivalries|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/09/01/the-10-best-college-rival_n_944635.html#s346513&title=Indiana_vs_Purdue|accessdate=7 May 2012|newspaper=Huffington Post|date=1 September 2011|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203232154/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/09/01/the-10-best-college-rival_n_944635.html#s346513&title=Indiana_vs_Purdue|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。此外，锅炉工和同州的[[圣母大学|圣母大学]]及邻州的[[伊利诺伊大学|伊利诺伊大学]]也是宿敌关系。它们的队歌是Hail Purdue（向普渡致敬）<ref>[http://purduesports.cstv.com/genrel/070904aab.html "Quick Facts"] {{Wayback|url=http://purduesports.cstv.com/genrel/070904aab.html |date=20070311150223 }}. Purdue Official Athletic Site. Accessed February 25, 2011.</ref>。“锅炉工”这个绰号也正体现了普渡大学的强项——工程类学科。

